{
  "stem": "20088.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 26.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russians have just been and they said they are coming back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, you know, it's too dangerous for you to stay here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he thought it was good enough in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he said, which way shall-- do we think shall I go?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she sent him the direction of into the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So later on when we-- we went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we came back and later on the Russians caught him, we saw that, and he was an SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because all the SS was tattooed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not [INAUDIBLE] only tattoo us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They tattooed the SS under the arm with some kind of a-- I don't know if it was a SS sign or number or something, but they were all marked.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they did shoot him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We saw that, that they shot this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But talking about-- so he didn't escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the camp when-- sometimes people did try to escape, but it wasn't because they wanted to escape or thought they can escape.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was really more a sign that they wanted to die and gave up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because none of the Jewish inmates ever did escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Occasionally a Pole did escape because they were sometimes even from the area and they knew people outside and they could speak the language and they might have known where to go.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So occasionally a Pole escaped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But from the Jews, never anybody escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- or when you went on a work commando and you walked outside, sometimes they just ran out of line.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were several things which happened to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they were shot because all their work commandos were walking with armed soldiers and soldiers with their dogs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So sometimes they were shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
